text:
I hereby to write an Compliments for Ms Estean Julea (2023 SEP to 2024 Dec) for her effort to take care the house.She was an very neat and well organised person and able to keep belongings to minimum.

What impressed me the most is she only got one shoes during her stay.

Hopefully she may venture further in her carrier.My family benefit from her character and wish to Shout out for her ^^
